name: EYE OF THOUGHT
description:
She haunts everyone, sooner or later, at least once in a lifetime.
This evil granny can always find you wherever you are.

Her name is a Terrible thought.

When you try to hide from her in the basement of your mind, you are unaware that you yourself are locking yourself inside your head.

Useless. 
It's no use trying to run away. You need to face this thought and not wait for help from somewhere above. 
Fight.

:: visuals: @cryptohamster | sound-design: @bisdvrk
